<Content>Cool vibe, Budget luxury- highly recommended! I love this hotel's concept- budget luxury and no rip offs. The prices are all reasonable- phone calls, in-room broadband, room service.. Nice for a change!My husband and I stayed here for one night just to check it out and would both highly recommend it. The hotel/rooms were very nicely decorated, the bathrooms very stylish and we liked the free take-away breakfast (Pret OJ, yoghurt with muesli and a banana- it's all you need really). The rooms are smallish, but perfect for a short stay or longer stay for one person. The hotel lobby bar was cozy and inviting, and the Caipirinha I ordered was one of the best I've had in a long while. There are lots of trendy bars and restaurants within walking distcance. We'll be back! 
